{"tid":1842371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 ！澳門決定抽調五萬個口罩俾珠海！真牛 b !","createTime":"2020-01-25T15:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T20:09:18.000Z","uid":118346,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8fdcbb51ee1d1d17daef8a54cf6ea9ba0caa4d","tid":1842371,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"支援珠海醫院抗疫口罩不影響澳門口罩派發計劃<br />\n<br />\n特區政府新型冠狀病毒感染應變協調中心表示，珠海醫院因醫用口罩缺貨，向澳門查詢能否作緊急支援。協調中心在評估澳門的口罩有足夠倉存後，決定抽調五萬個口罩給珠海醫院，供醫生應對疫情救急扶傷專用。協調中心強調，支援珠海醫院的口罩不會影響市民口罩的派發計劃，同時珠海攔截、控制新型肺炎個案並就地治療，有利於澳門的防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gov.mo/detail/zh-hant/N20AYcmr46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gov.mo%2Fdetail%2Fzh-hant%2FN20AYcmr46&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=39665a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.gov.mo/detail/zh-hant/N20AYcmr46</a>"},{"pid":"b4edce776b73f1958490e6e837bf8414695e7201","tid":1842371,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"反觀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c12e864e17fd6b693a5d54c65c931fc22e69880","tid":1842371,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"澳門市支持返自己省有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ea21869c8b61719df84e5b3ac9c0dad42381c5","tid":1842371,"uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b4edce776b73f1958490e6e837bf8414695e7201","tid":1842371,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"反觀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"澳門串到用唔哂俾大陸 ！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2b8fb134f58ba9bf1a5ff04f171fb2a45dbc28","tid":1842371,"uid":127177,"like":